# CODEOWNERS — Automatic PR Reviewer Assignment
# =====================================================
# Format: <file pattern>   <GitHub username(s) or team>
# When a PR changes a matching file, these people are auto-requested for review.
# With branch protection ON, their approval is REQUIRED to merge.
#
# Patterns use gitignore rules (most specific match wins).
# Replace @username placeholders with your real GitHub usernames/teams.
# =====================================================

# ─── Default: all files require QA lead review ──────────────────
*                               @your-github-username

# ─── All test files — QA team must review ────────────────────────
**/*test*.py                    @qa-team-lead

# ─── API tests — backend team + QA ──────────────────────────────
01_branching/api_tests.py       @backend-lead @qa-team-lead

# ─── Payment tests — sensitive, multiple reviewers ───────────────
03_merging/payment_tests.py     @backend-lead @qa-team-lead

# ─── GitHub Actions / CI ─────────────────────────────────────────
.github/                        @devops-lead @qa-team-lead

# ─── Configuration files ─────────────────────────────────────────
*.yml                           @devops-lead
*.yaml                          @devops-lead
.gitignore                      @your-github-username

# ─── Docs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
README.md                       @your-github-username
**/*.md                         @your-github-username
